850 A.2d 364 ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION OF MARYLAND, Petitioner v. Dennis G. OLVER, Respondent. Misc. Docket AG, No. 18,

Sept. Term, 2004.

Court of Appeals of Maryland. June 2, 2004.

In the Circuit Court for Baltimore City, Case No. 24-C-02-006710.

ORDER

This matter came before the Court on the Joint Petition for Placement on Inactive Status. Upon consideration of said petition, it is this 2nd day of June, 2004,

ORDERED that the Respondent Dennis G. Olver, be, and he is hereby, placed on inactive status until further Order of this Court and, it is further

ORDERED that the Clerk of this Court shall remove the name of Dennis G. Olver from the register of attorneys in this Court until further Order of this Court and shall certify that fact to the Client Protection Fund and the clerks of all judicial tribunals in this State in accordance with Maryland Rule 16-772(d).
